These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Flower         | poppy | sunflower  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Color   | blood-red       | fuchsia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: corn, cucumber
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, taxi
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Food           | corn | cucumber      |
| Transport   | taxi  | trike      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, august
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the nigerian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Birthday          | march    | august   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Nationality     | nigerian     | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, train
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Transport          | train         | van    |
| Cigar           | davidoff | game    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
There 2 different types of food: tomato, potato
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, security-guard
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the security-guard##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Food   | tomato | potato       |
| Sport         | sailing   | skateboarding |
| Job     | security-guard    | social-worker     |

