1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who likes lilac is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| Hobby         | reading            | board-games  |
| Pet           | dog | ferret |
| Color   | grey           | lilac       |
| Transport     | jet-ski            | trike        |

