.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Cigar           | bluemaster | siglo     |
| Sport   | rowing          | water-polo |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 